{
  "chapter": 32,
  "chapter_summary": "铁中棠被赤足汉击飞后落在方舟上，获麻衣客之母以内力疗伤。夫人修炼\"武道禅宗嫁衣神功\"十七年，真气强猛却无法运用，反因修炼而瘫痪。疗伤过程中，夫人数十年内力竟如江河决堤般灌入铁中棠体内，功力大增。夫人顿悟此功本为\"为他人作嫁衣裳\"，命铁中棠将秘册送给最自私残忍之人，并托他照顾麻衣客、寻找瞎眼女孩。铁中棠出战后震慑风九幽、卓三娘，轻易击败盛大娘。厅中风九幽与卓三娘联手围攻麻衣客，麻衣客渐处下风。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不……不追了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "你认输了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "text": "我若生得你那样矮小，轻功也未必输给你。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣客",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "轻功再好，也只是逃命本事，算不得什么手段。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "text": "你要比拼命的手段，不找风老四找谁，他想要你的命呀！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣客",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "正是要找他。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "text": "我也正要找你，抓着你还怕要不到那穿嫁衣裳的么？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们两位多打打，我进去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，莫要被她捡便宜先寻了去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "你要进去么？请！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "text": "狐狸精，又玩什么花样？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她……她还未死。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "叫你不要进去，你定要进去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "speaker_name": "水灵光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他还未死么？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_shui_ling_guang",
      "text": "小妹子，你那男人是活不成了，我们说的她，是另外一个人，这人你再也不会认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人既还未死，为何不出来相见？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "不错，我还未死，你可是要见我么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "没用的人，平日枉称了英雄。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，在下正要见夫人一面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你等着吧，我这就出来，说不定还将你们要的那东西带出来，你们可不要走呀！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然不走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黑袍妇人",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "text": "是……是她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_hei_pao_fu_ren",
      "text": "不错，是她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣客",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "家母请各位留下，谁敢走？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁要走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "text": "卓三娘，你走不走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "你不走，我怎舍得走。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你重伤之下，还不惜妄拼真力，一心要落在方舟之上，显见别有用心，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚辈内腑已被震伤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "若是无人打救，落水之后，必无生望，但晚辈年纪轻轻，实不想死。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你明知自身落入水中，我未必会将你救起，但你若落在我面前，我却不能见死不救了，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人明鉴，晚辈受的伤虽重，但夫人武功通神，自有回天之力，是以晚辈才存万一之想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你倒没说假话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你叫什么名字？可是大旗门下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你年纪轻轻，居然也会同情寂寞，这倒不易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "但你见了我的模样，怎不害怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚辈从不知道害怕，何况夫人具大智慧，大神通，自当将臭皮囊抛却，晚辈只有尊敬而已。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "皮相美丑，本乃智者不取，但当今世上，又有几个能不看皮相之人？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你还能动，便爬过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人莫非已肯垂怜相救？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你若非已受必死之伤，必定不敢擅自闯入来；你既凑巧来了，你我总是有缘，我好歹救你一命再说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "舟中可有人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人既然未死……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣客",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孽障！我要将他们骇走，他却偏要将之留住。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我既已有救你之心，为何不出手扶你一把，却看你在地上挣扎爬动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人莫非……已不能走动？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "这不干你事，快过来待我救好你伤势再说。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "多谢夫人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚辈不知夫人疗伤竟要损耗这许多内力，若是知道，晚辈也不敢妄求夫人了。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白……我明白了……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你闻得如此奇遇，非但不喜，反而惶恐，总算有些良心，何况……唉，此事本是天意，怪不得你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "但……但夫人怎……怎会将真……真气全都给……给了晚辈？叫晚辈好……好生不安。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "这原因委实奇妙古怪，此刻之前，连我也不知道是为了什么。唉，此刻我总算知道了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "这十七年来，我练的便是这'武道禅宗，嫁衣神功'。我虽早已知道这神功深奥并世无双，修练极难，但也知道只要练成此功之后，便将天下无敌，又听得昔年'大旗门'开山两位祖师，也因练成此功，遂至称雄天下，是以我才摒绝一切，下了狠心，决心来练它。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "这……这本神功秘册，莫非便是'大旗门'先人故意遗失的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "不错……但我一开始练此神功，便知不妙，只因一练此功之后，我体内真气，便忽然枯涩起来，难以运转，但那时我已欲罢不能，只有再练下去。哪知我真气虽越练越强，但若要它运转却是痛苦不堪，那真气流过之处，都宛如尖针所刺一般。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 415
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "那痛苦比世上任何苦刑都要难受，但若停止不练，功力立散，那散功之苦，实是非人能忍，是以明知是饮鸩止渴，也只有硬着头皮去练，而真力越强，痛苦越深，我只有将真气逼在丹田腹下，不让它随意运行，这时我下肢却已完全瘫了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "但真气纵然练得再强，如不能运用，又有何用？试想我对敌运用真气时，自身内脉已如针刺，怎能施展武功？我心中自痛苦不堪，但却百思不得其解，总以为自己必是练错了。再看这神功的名字，'嫁衣'两字，我虽始终不解，但'禅宗'两字，我却知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "佛家中'禅宗'最重'顿悟'，以传顿悟为第一大事。释迦牟尼说是：'微妙法门，不立文字，教外别传。'这神功既称武道中之禅宗，自是也以顿悟为重。顿悟乃立刻悟道之意，而我却苦练十余年，还是未得其旨，我昼夜苦思，越想越是糊涂，自己越是痛苦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "今日我虽是见你仁厚智高，不忍见你就死，是以才要以内力为你疗伤，但也是要看看我将体中的真气逼入你体中之后，你有何反应，否则我与你非亲非故，又怎肯不惜痛苦为你疗伤？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "哪知这令我痛苦不堪的真气，到了你体内，你竟行所无事，我心里奇怪，便将力道加强，这时你竟已将得自我的真气收为己用，与我相抗，但两种真气本属一源，自然互相吸引，而我之真气正在外流，便不知不觉被你吸了过去，等我发觉之时，我已欲罢不能，收不回了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 447
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是我内功虽失，却终于弄明白了一切，也高兴得很！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "原来这神功之名'嫁衣'两字，取的便是'为他人作嫁衣裳'之意。嫁衣缝成，让别人去穿，缝的人虽使千针万线，怎奈自己却不是新娘子，这神功练来也是要留给别人享用的。练的人虽然吃尽千辛万苦，自己却半分也用不上，这种功夫，难怪'大旗门'要将它远远丢开了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 459
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也知道了为何这神功要称'武道禅宗'，原来这'顿悟'两字，也是用在别人身上的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "但……但为何如此……为何这神功真气在夫人体中，便那般涩重，到了晚辈体中，便……便……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "想来必是因为这神功真气，太过强猛霸道，但经我十余年之磨炼，再入你身体之中，便将火烈之气，全都滤尽了，而两股同源真力互相吸引，乃是自然之理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天意……此功本属'大旗门'，你又是'大旗门'弟子，想来必是上天要你重振大旗门，才差你到这里来，否则你等纵然苦练三十年，也未见能复仇雪耻。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚辈深受夫人大恩，没齿难忘，夫人若不给晚辈报恩的机会，晚辈必将抱憾终天。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "报恩两字，本谈不上，你再也休要提起。但……但你若肯为我做几件事，我必当感激的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人只管吩咐，赴汤蹈火，在所不辞。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我儿子那些女弟子中，有个瞎眼的女孩子，这些年天天为我送饭，唉，她为了送饭给我，知道我不愿被外人所见，才自残双目，但愿你能为我找到这女孩子，替我好生谢谢她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚辈上天入地，也要将她寻着。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我儿子虽不孝，但总是我亲身所生，唉！这也怪我与他爹爹情怨纠缠，才令他左右为难，现在你功力已强胜于他，但愿你能照顾他，莫教他被别人杀死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚辈必将尊他为兄，互相规过劝善。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "好……好孩子。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "这'武道禅宗，嫁衣神功'你也带走，替我将它去送给一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "送……送给什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "去送给一个你所见过的人中，最最自私，最最残忍，从来不替别人着想的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我早已写下一封书信，夹在这秘册之中，你决定将之送给谁后，不妨拆开看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 531
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "我心愿仅止于此，但……唉，却还想见我那孽子一面，不知你可愿为我将他唤进来？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "但你却切切不可让第三者走上这方舟一步，我……我不愿别人见到我如此模样。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "你试试看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "平日你想捏扁这香炉难如登天，今日捏来却易如反掌，你可知这是什么原故？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "这只因我数十年性命交修之内功，已全被你吸收了去，再加上你本身功力，此时你功力之深，虽不敢说是震古铄今，天下无双，但当今武林之中，已少有人能及得上你了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哟，我可不敢问，风老四你去问吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "text": "她见了我就生气，还是你去吧，你看来总比我顺眼得多。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "speaker_name": "麻衣客",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你两人等得不耐，莫非是想先打一架么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "text": "小皇子，你真聪明，又让你猜对了，风老四想先宰了你哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "text": "宰你可不敢，打一架消遣消遣却不错。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小皇子，小心了，风老四阴风厉害得紧；风老四，你也小心了，小皇子'戏花拳'也不是好玩的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "风老四，你瞧小皇子已看上你，只是调戏你，你不如就嫁给他算了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这婆娘闲得太舒服了，倒要给她找点事做做……神斧力士何在？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zu_han",
      "speaker_name": "赤足汉",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "在！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_chi_zu_han",
      "text": "快跟她打上一架。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zu_han",
      "speaker_name": "赤足汉",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难怪雷老大说风老四不是坏人，只是疯子！但你也不想想，这大猴子碰得到我么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大猴子，快些呀……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对了，这样才热闹……哎哟，好招。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫骂，我公平得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_ma_yi_ke",
      "text": "再过五十招，要你躺下。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五十招不行，七十招却差不多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚……晚辈力所不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚……晚辈不知。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚辈该死，晚辈不知……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "不敢请……请问夫人……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_fu_ren",
      "text": "晚……晚辈身受大恩，实不知应该如何……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "此事你既无心，我亦非有意，怎能怪你，只是……只是这门神功，也未免对练功之人太残酷了些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "否则怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "否则就要你好看。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "text": "你若不将水姑娘快些还我，也和他一样。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 639
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怪事年年有，今年特别多，居然有个小伙子敢向'风梭'风九幽如此说话，端的妙极！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "text": "小伙子好没礼貌，风四太爷问你的话，你就该老老实实答出来，还敢反嘴？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "今日你老实说出如何将我幺叔弄来，再快快将他神智回复，倒也罢了，否则，哼哼！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhong_tang",
      "speaker_name": "铁中棠",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我问的话你两人快答复，否则莫怪我不客气了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "卓三娘",
      "listener": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "text": "这小子太过无礼，风老四，你还不教训教训他？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_jiu_you",
      "speaker_name": "风九幽",
      "listener": "char_zhuo_san_niang",
      "text": "三娘在此，小弟怎敢争先。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 32,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
